{"tid":631675,"cid":9,"subCid":0,"title":"[A/I] コトダマン言靈戰士 練日文學生字 共鬥拼字新Game","createTime":"2018-04-16T16:28:23.000Z","updateTime":"2018-04-29T15:46:23.000Z","uid":31242,"like":3,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":8,"replies":[{"pid":"82c811383e7fae76a6a60e25a1028628f74a3e43","tid":631675,"uid":31242,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-04-16T16:28:23.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2018/04/16/204359_6a2b98d60a7e543336d4a47a1aee0865.jpg\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2018%2F04%2F16%2F204359_6a2b98d60a7e543336d4a47a1aee0865.jpg&d=I72V8AtZztMkIY0Z8oawy5UJf0bKPU4tHf%2BJg0Yv85M%3D&h=831fbca6\" target=\"_blank\">https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2018/04/16/204359_6a2b98d60a7e543336d4a47a1aee0865.jpg</a><br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2018/04/17/001734_c270eb7dd0e8b6b2e46e7b8efb3a1362.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2018%2F04%2F17%2F001734_c270eb7dd0e8b6b2e46e7b8efb3a1362.jpg&h=e9a6e4f0&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n本作是一款使用「言語」戰鬥的新感覺RPG，最大可實現4人共鬥！<br />\n<br />\n戰鬥系統幾有創意，遊戲畫面見上圖，填50音睇下夾埋可以組到幾多個單字(=幾多combo)，如果單字由3/4個50音就可以發動技能<br />\n<br />\n玩左陣覺得隻驚真係可以令你識到好多意想不到嘅偏門生字<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n另外提返聲，唔識日文，尤其係連50音基本知識都無就只有鳩擺，一定會無晒樂趣<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/25.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n新手教學有少少長，但唔使down data刷唔刷見仁見智<br />\n<br />\n教學10抽一定出其中一隻屬嘅5星<br />\n<img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2018/04/17/002107_f8728cbc7fddcb1087bd3ff734d651e9.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2018%2F04%2F17%2F002107_f8728cbc7fddcb1087bd3ff734d651e9.png&h=12fddf05&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n之後去禮物箱拎1000石果10抽先係真正首抽，評價可以睇住哩個網下面先，5星出率5%<br />\n<a href=\"https://kotodaman.gamerch.com/リセマラ当たりランキング\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fkotodaman.gamerch.com%2F%E3%83%AA%E3%82%BB%E3%83%9E%E3%83%A9%E5%BD%93%E3%81%9F%E3%82%8A%E3%83%A9%E3%83%B3%E3%82%AD%E3%83%B3%E3%82%B0&d=I72V8AtZztMkIY0Z8oawy5UJf0bKPU4tHf%2BJg0Yv85M%3D&h=839e637b\" target=\"_blank\">https://kotodaman.gamerch.com/リセマラ当たりランキング</a><br />\n<br />\n刷首抽方法︰主頁&gt;右下角 &gt;アカウントリセット<br />\n<br />\n另外隻game有所謂招待code，雖然我未知有咩用<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n<strong>最後最後，暫時上手覺得戰鬥系統幾有新意，但實際上其他位(eg養成果啲)感覺都係同果啲速食game大同小異<br />\n我好懷疑可唔可以靠一個拼生字嘅玩法帶起成隻game，如果唔係感覺都係3日貨仔，玩到對拼字無晒興趣就會棄</strong>"},{"pid":"cb5f0a3e363a7a062fb2c060d137863eb4a0a2a3","tid":631675,"uid":31242,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-04-16T16:50:30.000Z","msg":"我都知半夜開post無人留意，係咁意推下<br />\n<br />\n係Qoo見到，事前竟然係用聯動角色<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/surprise.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n日本 SEGA 今天（16）推出了拼字新作《言靈戰士》（iOS/Android）並且宣佈所有事前登錄條件均已達成，所有玩家將可得到超人力霸王、七色的靈刃使以及芭月涼等角色！"},{"pid":"ffc01aa99ea91cd1fbe459dca7ea740f4136e86e","tid":631675,"uid":43802,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-04-17T01:53:39.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/tongue.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/tongue.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"d68086c88320eae57464d925a3fc64aa53deb6ff","tid":631675,"uid":31242,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"ffc01aa99ea91cd1fbe459dca7ea740f4136e86e","tid":631675,"uid":43802,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-04-17T01:53:39.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/tongue.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/tongue.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2018-04-17T04:15:33.000Z","msg":"完全無人<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n雖然生字識得唔夠多係玩得無癮"},{"pid":"e0748905c8659d900c58e54dadab465826a86c80","tid":631675,"uid":23829,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"d68086c88320eae57464d925a3fc64aa53deb6ff","tid":631675,"uid":31242,"like":0,"dis